title: (x) Coyotes high school team - similar to FF Trademarker {Tiff}
content:
Hey Guys!   
   
I need some help identifying this font PLEASE!   
   
 ![Coyotes home](http://web.archive.org/web/20050819144018im_/http:/www.typophile.com/forums/messages/83/48707.jpg)
author: thegetdown

comments.content:
Tony, Is this from a professional sports team?   
   
If so that would explain (probably) why no one has ID'd it. Most pro team logos and lettering are custom font designs and may only have been lettered for those words, without necessarily developing a complete font.   
   
Let's see if anyone else knows, but that might explain the slow thread.

Naaaw Mike, it was an old logo from a high school team, I assumed they used a font rather than something custom. I'll try the Trademark font with some adjustments.   
   
Thanks!
